column5: My wife Georgia, our son Henry and I would be excited to welcome you into our home. You'll have a private room and bathroom and use of common areas. The McKinney square, with live music, food, shops and bars is walkable, and access to DFW is easy.  We are excited to welcome people from all walks of life. People of color and LGBT folks are always welcome in our home.
column8: Cozy Bungalow, walk from McKinney Square
